@ChatService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5056

GET {{ChatService_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

### Start chat with seller
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}"
}

###

### Send message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/{{chatId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Привіт! Цікавить цей товар, чи є знижки?"
}

###

### Get my chats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/my-chats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get specific chat
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/{{chatId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get chat messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/{{chatId}}/messages?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
